  "detailed_description": "<strong>In this VR experience, take on the role of a transplant surgeon facing the challenge of performing surgery on aliens and cyborgs in a dystopian world. Use the diverse tools at your disposal to solve environmental surgery puzzles using your mechanical arms. And stay alert... you never know what dangers lie within.</strong><br><br><br>In a dystopian future where aliens, cyborgs, and humans coexist, healthy organs are the new currency. You embody Cuz, a specialist in the art of trans-species surgery, faced with conditions that could only be described as… unconventional. Alongside your AI partner Walt, you are drawn into a critical endeavour to thwart the sinister plans of a hate-mongering priest to save an alien race from his clutches.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• The Bee Bus</h2>Not your average medical transport. Command this nimble vessel to traverse the biological landscape within your patients, reaching areas otherwise inaccessible by foot.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/c237e136fa846664d152de12c230ca37.poster.avif?t=1728481653\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/c237e136fa846664d152de12c230ca37.webm?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/c237e136fa846664d152de12c230ca37.mp4?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• The Tools</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scanner</h2>A diagnostic tool designed to probe environmental elements, providing crucial information and insights that aid in puzzle resolution.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/0ee9bcc479cfbf9ff166d42da32d898a.poster.avif?t=1728481653\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/0ee9bcc479cfbf9ff166d42da32d898a.webm?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/0ee9bcc479cfbf9ff166d42da32d898a.mp4?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grasper</h2>Extend your reach with this tool, designed to retrieve items beyond normal grasp and manipulate objects with precision and ease.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/a37910172bcf78789c9cf94aec358054.poster.avif?t=1728481653\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/a37910172bcf78789c9cf94aec358054.webm?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/a37910172bcf78789c9cf94aec358054.mp4?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scalpel</h2>Designed to deliver accurate and controlled cuts, this tool allows you to delicately sever veins to redirect blood flow, while also serving as a formidable weapon against adversaries.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/1824e1302d4201acbf9ac3ea182b2f28.poster.avif?t=1728481653\" width=620 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/1824e1302d4201acbf9ac3ea182b2f28.webm?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/1824e1302d4201acbf9ac3ea182b2f28.mp4?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drill</h2>Engineered to dismantle crystalline formations and bodily build-ups, this drill enables access to concealed materials and organs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/9e8dee096c6698e2a02b9a8ebd18b69c.poster.avif?t=1728481653\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/9e8dee096c6698e2a02b9a8ebd18b69c.webm?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/9e8dee096c6698e2a02b9a8ebd18b69c.mp4?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Syringe</h2>Used for extracting and harnessing natural substances like acids, antibiotics, and anti-inflammatories from the surrounding environment. Employ these fluids in treatment to rejuvenate and heal patient tissues.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/b89e7aebad947ba6a9a0233fe013975d.poster.avif?t=1728481653\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/b89e7aebad947ba6a9a0233fe013975d.webm?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/b89e7aebad947ba6a9a0233fe013975d.mp4?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Laser</h2>A dual-purpose device, pivotal for cauterizing wounds to halt bleeding and for providing a line of defense against distant threats.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/8aeb8c547dfa324a0254eee649f68016.poster.avif?t=1728481653\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/8aeb8c547dfa324a0254eee649f68016.webm?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/8aeb8c547dfa324a0254eee649f68016.mp4?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>In this VR experience, take on the role of a transplant surgeon facing the challenge of performing surgery on aliens and cyborgs in a dystopian world. Use the diverse tools at your disposal to solve environmental surgery puzzles using your mechanical arms. And stay alert... you never know what dangers lie within.</strong><br><br><br>In a dystopian future where aliens, cyborgs, and humans coexist, healthy organs are the new currency. You embody Cuz, a specialist in the art of trans-species surgery, faced with conditions that could only be described as… unconventional. Alongside your AI partner Walt, you are drawn into a critical endeavour to thwart the sinister plans of a hate-mongering priest to save an alien race from his clutches.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• The Bee Bus</h2>Not your average medical transport. Command this nimble vessel to traverse the biological landscape within your patients, reaching areas otherwise inaccessible by foot.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/c237e136fa846664d152de12c230ca37.poster.avif?t=1728481653\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/c237e136fa846664d152de12c230ca37.webm?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/c237e136fa846664d152de12c230ca37.mp4?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• The Tools</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scanner</h2>A diagnostic tool designed to probe environmental elements, providing crucial information and insights that aid in puzzle resolution.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/0ee9bcc