cbf9ac3ea182b2f28.mp4?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drill</h2>Engineered to dismantle crystalline formations and bodily build-ups, this drill enables access to concealed materials and organs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/9e8dee096c6698e2a02b9a8ebd18b69c.poster.avif?t=1728481653\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/9e8dee096c6698e2a02b9a8ebd18b69c.webm?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/9e8dee096c6698e2a02b9a8ebd18b69c.mp4?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Syringe</h2>Used for extracting and harnessing natural substances like acids, antibiotics, and anti-inflammatories from the surrounding environment. Employ these fluids in treatment to rejuvenate and heal patient tissues.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/b89e7aebad947ba6a9a0233fe013975d.poster.avif?t=1728481653\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/b89e7aebad947ba6a9a0233fe013975d.webm?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/b89e7aebad947ba6a9a0233fe013975d.mp4?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Laser</h2>A dual-purpose device, pivotal for cauterizing wounds to halt bleeding and for providing a line of defense against distant threats.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/8aeb8c547dfa324a0254eee649f68016.poster.avif?t=1728481653\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/8aeb8c547dfa324a0254eee649f68016.webm?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331420/extras/8aeb8c547dfa324a0254eee649f68016.mp4?t=1728481653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
